Package: GlosendaR
Title: Download GPS Tracking Data from the Glosendas OrniTrack Portal
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple interface to authenticate with the Glosendas 
    OrniTrack wildlife tracking portal (https://cpanel.glosendas.net) and 
    download GPS and sensor data for tagged animals. Supports filtering by 
    species or any keyword, all available data formats (GPS, sensors, V1/V2), 
    custom date ranges, and returns a tidy data frame ready for analysis.
